column2: b'Lupin III: Tenshi no Tactics - Yume no Kakera wa Koroshi no Kaori'

b'Stolen from the famous "secret" Air Force base, Area 51, Lupin\'s most recently stolen treasure holds a secret. Four "Bloody Angels," the toughest women Lupin has ever faced, want the treasure for their own terrorist purposes. Meanwhile Zenigata teams up with a female police officer to hunt Lupin and the terrorists down.\n\n(Source: ANN)'
